data.description: 5 Bedroom, 3 Full Bath PLUS Bonus Room / Office!! Established neighborhood * NO HOA! * HUGE fenced yard w/ no immediate neighbors behind! * Incredible natural light in the Kitchen w/ cutest bay-window breakfast nook overlooking the backyard * Spacious primary bedroom w/ walk-in-closet & private bath w/ double vanity * Brand new Refrigerator * ALL appliances stay including brand new washer & dryer, deep freeze, and extra fridge * Trash service and pest service paid in advance through February! * Covered front & back porches * 2 Car Garage * Storage building * Home warranty offered by Seller * So much space, so much to offer with this home! Located in a quiet neighborhood with large yards and mature shade trees. Ask your agent for the extra details on this home! (kitchen island doesn't convey) ***Seller willing to have new carpet installed w/ accepted offer, to be installed after closing!!***
